'''斯庫皮'''（Scupi）是位於[[北馬其頓共和國|北馬其頓共和國]][[斯科普里|斯科普里]]郊區的一個考古遺址<ref>{{cite book|title=Dictionary of Greek and Roman Geography|editor-first=William|editor-last=Smith|editor-link=威廉·史密斯_(辞书编纂家)|place=London|publisher=Walton and Maberly, Upper Gower Street and Ivy Lane, Paternoster Row; John Murray, Albemarle Street|year=1854|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0064%3Aalphabetic+letter%3DS%3Aentry+group%3D8%3Aentry%3Dscupi-geo|chapter=Scupi|access-date=2015-10-02|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918093032/http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0064%3Aalphabetic+letter%3DS%3Aentry+group%3D8%3Aentry%3Dscupi-geo|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=[[Ptolemy|Ptolemy]]|title=[[Geography_(Ptolemy)|Geography]]|chapter=III.9.6|chapter-url=https://archive.org/stream/bub_gb_4ksBAAAAMAAJ#page/n214/mode/1up|language=el}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=[[Stephanus_of_Byzantium|Stephanus of Byzantium]]|title=Ethnika kat' epitomen|url=https://archive.org/stream/stephanibyzanti00meingoog#page/n590/mode/1up|chapter=Σκοῦποι|language=el}}</ref>。斯庫皮是一個羅馬帝國時期的考古遺址。西元518年時，斯庫皮被地震摧毀，之後被廢棄。
